rows.label: qst700202_msg0001
rows.name:
Meh? Friends have business with
Dekudeku?

rows.label: qst700202_msg0002
rows.name:
Ah, indeed, it true. Dekudeku on
Walky-Walky pilgrimage, special rite
of passage for Voltis Trade Guild.

rows.label: qst700202_msg0003
rows.name:
Is making only minor impression, me
know, but please to realize Dekudeku
carrying future of trade guild on back!

rows.label: qst700202_msg0004
rows.name:
It take budding young...aspiring...
merchant like self to generate strong
cash flow!

rows.label: qst700202_msg0005
rows.name:
Meh-meh? Friends take interest in
Dekudeku and need to ask favor?

rows.label: qst700202_msg0006
rows.name:
So textile shop doing poor business
and asking Dekudeku to invest...

rows.label: qst700202_msg0008
rows.name:
This perfect opportunity to put
financial skills to test!

rows.label: qst700202_msg0009
rows.name:
But not to expect results immediately.
Dekudeku need time to draw up
business plan.

rows.label: qst700202_msg0010
rows.name:
Is no easy road to success. Get rich
quick scheme is pie in sky way of
thinking, even if sound delicious.

rows.label: qst700202_msg0011
rows.name:
OK, Dekudeku go ahead and have talk
with manager now.

rows.label: qst700202_msg0012
rows.name:
Fully understanding situation is key to
every successful business transaction!

rows.label: qst700202_msg0013
rows.name:
Will consider options on table and
get back to friends when return!

rows.label: qst700202_msg0101
rows.name:
First plan of action is make two types
of hat and establish sales plan!

rows.label: qst700202_msg0102
rows.name:
Friends can assist by delivering
materials to owner!

rows.label: qst700202_msg0103
rows.name:
Supply material ultimately form
cornerstone and decide whether
business sink or float!
